This is a main project of U.S. congress info platform (web version)
Collaboration of:
Frontend:
  Static: HTML5 CSS3 (basic display)
  Dynamic: JavaScript (logic)
Backend: PHP (proxy)
Framework: Bootstrap3 and AngularJS (elaborate display and MVC manipulation)
API: Sunlight Congress JSON formatted open API
Web server: AWS (configured Elastic Beanstalk)
User Experience: Ajax pre-fetching and Responsive Design (desktop and mobile)

Shout out @specialfafa for his awesome open source plugin: dirPagination using AngularJS.
